♪The rift in time and space
is deftly manipulated♪

2
00:00:17,660 --> 00:00:21,100
♪Dark clouds roil,
malice lurking and waiting♪

3
00:00:21,460 --> 00:00:25,260
♪I roar, stirring a wild tempest
on the ground♪

4
00:00:29,180 --> 00:00:32,580
