even venturing where dragons be♪

14
00:01:19,460 --> 00:01:26,340
♪This battle's not in vain,
for the light that I maintain♪

15
00:01:29,620 --> 00:01:32,070
[Hero Is Back]

16
00:01:32,070 --> 00:01:35,940
